Our modal of choice is called JQuery Model and this option is writen to work with it.
To install JQuery Model please follow the instruction laid out in here  JQuery Modal Installation Guide .  After you have installed JQuery Modal copy the below HTML into your websites HTML on the pages you'd like it to be used. We recommened adding to your websites main layout page just before the closing  </body>  tag. Jquery Modal HTML   <div id="oxipay-modal" style="display:none;">
    <iframe id="oxipay-external" src="https://oxipay.com.au/externalmodal" style="
        width: 100%;
        height: 70vh;
        border: none;
      "></iframe>
  </div>
